	C wrappers.

2006-06-08  Stanislav Brabec  <sbrabec@suse.cz>

	* *-config: Added support for more arguments. Enabled support
	for all deprecated gtk2 functions.

	* *glade*, *xml*: Added support for libxml and libglade.

	* *.m4: Force GTK2 objects in M4 files.

	* *.h: Added some wrapper header files.

	* *.c: Created a static library with removed or not exported
	functions.

	* scripts/gtk1-compat-autofix: Added.

